history.content:
If you’re looking for some advice on class recommendations or just life at Cal in general, join IEEE from 6-7PM PDT on Wednesday, April 7th for an insightful speed mentoring workshop! You will have the opportunity to talk to upperclassmen mentors for 15 minutes at a time on any of these topics and more.

 

Please sign up for the event with the link: http://bit.ly/ieee-mentoring-signup

 

We will use the interactive gather.town platform at: http://bit.ly/ieee-mentoring-gathertown

 

See you at Speed Mentoring!
